    "body" : "<p>To quote <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/9/docs/api/java/lang/Class.html#newInstance--\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Java 9's javadoc</a>:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>The call</p>\n  \n  <p><code>clazz.newInstance()</code></p>\n  \n  <p>can be replaced by</p>\n  \n  <p><code>clazz.getDeclaredConstructor().newInstance()</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n"
